```plantuml
@startuml Taymindis_fcgi-function

component "Web Server (Nginx/Apache)" as webserver {
    component "FastCGI Interface" as fcgi_interface
}

component "FastCGI Function Handler" as ffunc {
    component "Request Dispatcher" as dispatcher {
        component "Function Mapper" as mapper
        component "Thread Pool Manager" as thread_pool
    }
    
    component "Memory Pool" as mem_pool
    component "Platform Adapter" as platform_adapter
}

component "User Functions" as user_functions {
    component "Profile Service" as profile_service
    component "Other Handlers" as other_handlers
}

webserver --> ffunc : FastCGI protocol
ffunc --> user_functions : Function calls

dispatcher --> mapper : maps FN_HANDLER to\nfunction pointer
dispatcher --> thread_pool : manages worker threads
dispatcher --> mem_pool : allocates request memory
dispatcher --> platform_adapter : OS-specific operations

mapper --> user_functions : resolves handlers
thread_pool --> user_functions : executes in threads

note right of ffunc
    Control Flow Highlights:
    1. Web server forwards requests via FastCGI
    2. Dispatcher routes to appropriate handler
    3. Thread pool enables concurrent execution
    4. Memory pool optimizes allocations
end note

@enduml
```